# Future Roadmap â€“ Awaken Platform

The GEC system serves as the technical foundation for the future **Awaken Platform**.

Planned enhancements include:
- Cloud-based administration portal
- Multi-site and multi-tenant support
- Secure REST APIs
- Online reservation integration (e.g., Skedda)
- Automated PIN generation
- Analytics and reporting dashboards
- Cross-platform client support

Awaken is designed to scale nationally while maintaining open-access principles for public institutions.
